May require balancing immediate &amp; long term reward</p>

<h2 id="importance-of-reward-function">Importance of reward function</h2>

<ul>
  <li>RL tents to overfit toward easier problem!</li>
  <li>
    <p>So we should design reward function seriously</p>
  </li>
  <li>Each time step t:
    <ul>
      <li>Agent takes an action $a_t$</li>
      <li>World updates given action $a_t$ then omits observation $o_t$ and reward $r_t$</li>
      <li>Agent receives $a_t$ and $o_t$</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>History $h_t$ = $(a_1 , o_1, r_1 … , a_t , o_t, r_t )$</p>

<p>Agent decides action based on history</p>

